{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 10:10Figure 10: Radial performance profiles for three representative proto-halos (H1, H2, H3 from table8; columns from left to right).",
    "Rows display (top to bottom) accuracy, false positive rate (FPR), completeness, and purity as functions of distance from the true center of mass.",
    "Solid, dashed, and dotted lines correspond to vipr, copra, and pinocchio, respectively.",
    "The vertical dotted line marks the Lagrangian radius R Lag.",
    "The profiles are shown out to the maximum proto-halo extent R max."
  ]
}